    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small scuff on the rear bumper\u2014typical for a vehicle enjoyed on the open road. Inside, the cabin is a smoke-free environment featuring supple leather upholstery with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the dual-zone climate control, functions exactly as it should. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; the engine pulls strongly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and the suspension remains firm and quiet over bumps. It has been serviced regularly, with a fresh oil change and a recent brake inspection performed just last month. The tires have approximately 70% tread remaining, ensuring you're ready for the seasons ahead. This is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner to drive home today.",
